caption.body: Tom Elliot and Simon Reichel train their lens on The Gare at the mouth of the River Tees in England’s industrial northeast, where surfers brave freezing waters and industrial pollution to ride the breakers of a coastline better known for its refineries and steel mills.  See "Through Clouds and Water” by A Common Future, now playing, in the Video Arts Gallery, located, pre-security, in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2CRe2vJ
